<abstract>
<p>While chronic pain is a major challenge to clinicians, advances in epigentics and analytical hypnotherapy provide both an understanding of how they develop and the means to bring relief. Many of these conditions are based on faulty subconscious belief systems as a result of early life imprints — particularly in reference to spiritual issues. A brief explanation of Medical Hypnoanalysis and its usefulness is provided in a case history in which the underlying dynamics are discussed and followed to a successful outcome.</p>
</abstract>
